<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201109/2651f34742c442b3923d7a1a3a01ee0c.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">山水 136x68cm 2020年</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201109/938c8d6000b5440eba328fdf51a59e59.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">长城 190x150cm 2018年</span></img></p>
